{"tid":649511,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【連登女神】親自操刀！莊思敏晒着和服相激似日本妹","createTime":"2018-05-01T15:40:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-01T19:17:40.000Z","uid":33176,"like":1,"dislike":54,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ed56df1ce50fb63d0981d56048b084dec62e1848","tid":649511,"uid":33176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T15:40:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180430/photo/bkn-20180430074429599-0430_00862_001_01p.jpg?20180430100641\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180430%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180430074429599-0430_00862_001_01p.jpg%3F20180430100641&h=aabc5dfa&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n自己影又真係幾靚喎！ <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n藝人莊思敏（Jacquelin）正在日本青森旅行，當地正值櫻花盛開嘅季節，Jacquelin當然把握機會瘋狂自拍。Jacquelin呢日喺社交網上載咗一系列嘅旅行靚相，見佢先以一身白色和服嘅造型，喺櫻花樹下不停影相，仲拎埋紙傘做道具，真係十足十日本妹！之後Jacquelin轉戰神社，換上粉紅色和服嘅佢喪扮甫士，仲落力到瞓上石枱添！Jacquelin除咗做model出色，原來影相都有一手，佢大爆原來呢輯旅行相係自己親自操刀，即獲網民大讚佢攝影技術了得，完全睇唔出係自拍嘅作品。 <br />\n<br />\nJacquelin表示：「我都係第一次睇櫻花，因為之前幾次想睇，都遇唔啱個花期。着和服都係第一次，原來着和服好複雜，起碼要兩個人幫手，仲要着半個鐘。」她稱今次只逗留四天，笑言當地與平時認知的日本很不同：「呢度好鄉下，冇得shopping又冇乜好嘢食，真係嚟睇景，所以好少香港人嚟。」回港後，Jacquelin便要投入工作，她透露正洽談一套內地劇集，稍後會客串一套電影。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180430/photo/bkn-20180430074429599-0430_00862_001_02b.jpg?20180430100641\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180430%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180430074429599-0430_00862_001_02b.jpg%3F20180430100641&h=1e46a177&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nJacquelin Chok到爆！ <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180430/photo/bkn-20180430074429599-0430_00862_001_03b.jpg?20180430100641\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180430%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180430074429599-0430_00862_001_03b.jpg%3F20180430100641&h=9f63c450&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n個景咁靚點可以唔影相。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180430/photo/bkn-20180430074429599-0430_00862_001_04b.jpg?20180430100641\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180430%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180430074429599-0430_00862_001_04b.jpg%3F20180430100641&h=ae7bf327&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nJacquelin話佢係第一次着和服。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180430/photo/bkn-20180430074429599-0430_00862_001_05b.jpg?20180430100641\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180430%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180430074429599-0430_00862_001_05b.jpg%3F20180430100641&h=2f5e9600&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n睇櫻花都係第一次。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180430/photo/bkn-20180430074429599-0430_00862_001_06b.jpg?20180430100641\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180430%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180430074429599-0430_00862_001_06b.jpg%3F20180430100641&h=77403f28&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之前試過想睇櫻花，不過撞唔啱花期。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180430/photo/bkn-20180430074429599-0430_00862_001_07b.jpg?20180430100641\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180430%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180430074429599-0430_00862_001_07b.jpg%3F20180430100641&h=f6655a0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n神社都係一個好靚嘅景點。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180430/photo/bkn-20180430074429599-0430_00862_001_08b.jpg?20180430100641\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180430%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180430074429599-0430_00862_001_08b.jpg%3F20180430100641&h=157051c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nJacquelin笑言呢度冇得shopping，所以唔多香港人。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180430/photo/bkn-20180430074429599-0430_00862_001_09b.jpg?20180430100641\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180430%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180430074429599-0430_00862_001_09b.jpg%3F20180430100641&h=945534e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n瞓住嚟影。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180430/photo/bkn-20180430074429599-0430_00862_001_10b.jpg?20180430100641\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180430%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180430074429599-0430_00862_001_10b.jpg%3F20180430100641&h=62f6fd76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n返香港就要投入工作。"},{"pid":"3faaaba505bf180078dc536fc8e640fbbc9cd548","tid":649511,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T15:41:21.000Z","msg":"最完美女人之一"},{"pid":"0c9d67493022b6cc8f1c138b4eb0bef0b8ed69a1","tid":649511,"uid":82917,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T15:42:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/01/234218_565e34174f139f72e4810d225f0aa67b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F01%2F234218_565e34174f139f72e4810d225f0aa67b.png&h=4124a33b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c6a8c626853bd5aed033778b3c7d012abc262b1e","tid":649511,"uid":37666,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T15:42:58.000Z","msg":"篇文佢比錢請人寫架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b58ecca730193333bca8573ea6c9558810a495f","tid":649511,"uid":117729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T15:43:10.000Z","msg":"青森點會無野食..."},{"pid":"47030591066435d9a55ce60d58425fd1217d4b1e","tid":649511,